[{"Code":"en","Title":"Hana Virtual Account (pilot)","Slug":"hana-virtual-account","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"763c044f-d0be-4374-947c-7810d1cac1e3\"><img data-block-id=\"5b01429e-04c3-451e-a648-ee12ad99d661\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(69).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" title=\"image(69).png\" width=\"277\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:277px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"186bc212-4f89-4c6d-9d91-b52c32678e13\">Hana Virtual Account is a reliable payment method from one of Indonesia's international banking networks. It’s s provided by Hana Bank Indonesia, a subsidiary of South Korea's Hana Financial Group, known for its strong corporate banking services and cross-border transaction capabilities in Indonesia.</p><p data-block-id=\"afbb93b3-4f91-49c2-bd54-ea8a525148ee\">When customers choose Hana VA during checkout, they receive a unique virtual account number. They can then complete the payment through Hana Bank's mobile banking app, internet banking platform, ATMs, or at any Hana Bank branch location. The payment is confirmed automatically once the customer transfers the exact amount to the provided virtual account number.</p><hr class=\"hr-divider1\"><h2 data-block-id=\"6146dcc6-4245-4158-a034-de0971f8c50b\">Features</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"523\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:523px;width:523px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:235px;\"><col style=\"width:288px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\"><p data-block-id=\"db4dfef8-c563-4305-8c29-ef2b1aa63d40\"><strong>Channel code</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"288\"><p data-block-id=\"396eeeac-4ec3-4dcb-9d87-03dfbc708fe4\"><code>HANA_VIRTUAL_ACCOUNT</code></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\"><p data-block-id=\"05742465-0957-4c43-b4a1-a714d1ec5bd9\"><strong>Currency</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"288\"><p data-block-id=\"089d5743-8152-4ba6-8397-606b6cec62d6\">IDR</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\"><p data-block-id=\"216547ce-9149-4c98-863b-af7a9b417559\"><strong>Minimum amount</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"288\"><p data-block-id=\"9f11a493-657e-4f53-8200-664b29cbb4d0\">1</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\"><p data-block-id=\"917595fc-cd1e-4638-a3ac-8c763018c400\"><strong>Maximum amount</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"288\"><p data-block-id=\"050f0c67-b03f-4f17-88cb-fe412010855b\">50,000,000,000</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\"><p data-block-id=\"dd693bd7-6fa5-470c-a762-3bd25581ee55\"><strong>User approval flow</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"288\"><p data-block-id=\"6c3485e2-8be5-421b-8f58-5cffed379b08\">PRESENT TO CUSTOMER</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\"><p data-block-id=\"00b142a2-96d8-469f-a603-d7f653f2f6a6\"><strong>Reusable payment code</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"288\"><p data-block-id=\"4539fce0-abba-4afc-a78b-9edd62506ad7\">✅</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\"><p data-block-id=\"a15e3b11-bb7c-4496-bbdd-cbc61b5faf78\"><strong>Custom payment code</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"288\"><p data-block-id=\"fee79fe7-3031-47a6-a8a4-e343701d0de7\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\"><p data-block-id=\"d4fc461e-77d4-4e93-b6a4-95652e301b57\"><strong>Display merchant name</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"288\"><p data-block-id=\"7ee79971-f5d3-47f9-b56c-c662acc7bb3d\">MERCHANT</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\"><p data-block-id=\"260ee695-3783-478d-b6ce-168812cf5235\"><strong>Display user name</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"288\"><p data-block-id=\"c089f673-06d7-409d-a611-15d4b735faad\">✅</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\"><p data-block-id=\"ebe59eaf-3581-4b5e-9133-086846171bc3\"><strong>Set expiry</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"288\"><p data-block-id=\"12be7429-c7c7-4479-b81b-04da759b7fef\">✅</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\"><p data-block-id=\"7750e331-7b15-4423-9ba5-f771994775fe\"><strong>Settlement time</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"288\"><p data-block-id=\"cfc1be6f-af22-48f6-bbf6-534529b76da5\">Instant</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\"><p data-block-id=\"6779fc15-6426-43e4-83b0-b2e6307dba73\"><strong>Refund</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"288\"><p data-block-id=\"d6dac5f5-cc08-448c-a14b-4b4811a5274f\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\"><p data-block-id=\"0baabc7e-a92b-49d0-af45-796c16289f04\"><strong>Partial refund</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"288\"><p data-block-id=\"3db5ce35-df38-47d0-8955-bd2e0dbfbc23\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\"><p data-block-id=\"166f9598-76a9-48a7-b24b-9c06b9f896ce\"><strong>Multiple partial refund</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"288\"><p data-block-id=\"e0def918-8005-4a4e-b489-d49d65943b1a\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\"><p data-block-id=\"256467fa-b7fd-45f2-b88e-195088282404\"><strong>Refund validity</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"288\"><p data-block-id=\"36880c22-7833-45f4-b3b2-ca7bb0454f6c\">N/A</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\"><p data-block-id=\"5c93e485-a74d-4a50-8a1b-9bba2a9f420b\"><strong>Compatible integration</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"288\"><p data-block-id=\"a65b438c-71f6-40d0-a937-5a7d8672ccf9\">Payment API, Payment Links</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"2b081c08-ffd2-493a-b253-c4931f5f1c75\">How to pay</h2><div class=\"details-wrapper details-wrapper_rendered\" data-type=\"details-wrapper\"><details data-opened=\"true\" data-button-align=\"right\" data-details-border=\"withBorder\" data-expand-icon=\"arrow\" data-lock=\"false\"><summary><p data-block-id=\"2489516d-1747-4d6a-a095-881709940e75\">Mobile banking</p></summary><div><div><ol data-block-id=\"cf040642-e442-46df-8880-55c9973f092a\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"fb36bac3-d049-4a41-ad7a-be653a95c497\"><p data-block-id=\"249aec70-31be-4e17-bd42-b0e4cce850fe\">Log in to LINE Bank mobile app</p></li><li data-block-id=\"740e71e2-f26a-40ac-81c5-88f7004aaa98\"><p data-block-id=\"639db83f-d2e4-4a10-916a-4e5137350287\">Select <strong>Top Up &amp; Bill &gt; Hana Bank Virtual Account</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"dcaa91e9-2062-450a-ae89-5cd0673683b2\"><p data-block-id=\"8a63d3cf-3a42-4c35-ae63-c9aa25058b46\">Enter virtual account number (e.g. 9010001112341234234)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"31329550-e8fe-411c-a270-d0f3ab256bd5\"><p data-block-id=\"76f8875b-88d5-413e-8c19-68ee923fd2a2\">Confirm payment details</p></li><li data-block-id=\"e8368295-a0d0-4dad-bce3-c15e08b07a22\"><p data-block-id=\"5b32b875-dd48-4c15-92af-ca1016b01b9f\">Enter PIN</p></li></ol></div></div></details><button class=\"details-arrow\" type=\"details\"></button></div><p data-block-id=\"f6d84e8d-d1d9-4945-9916-4b63220d8b3d\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Hana Virtual Account (pilot)","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Akun Virtual Hana (pilot)","Slug":"hana-virtual-accounts","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"763c044f-d0be-4374-947c-7810d1cac1e3\"><img data-block-id=\"5b01429e-04c3-451e-a648-ee12ad99d661\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(69).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" title=\"image(69).png\" width=\"277\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:277px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"186bc212-4f89-4c6d-9d91-b52c32678e13\">Hana Virtual Account adalah metode pembayaran yang andal dari salah satu jaringan perbankan internasional di Indonesia. Layanan ini disediakan oleh Hana Bank Indonesia, anak perusahaan dari Hana Financial Group Korea Selatan, yang dikenal dengan layanan perbankan korporat yang kuat dan kapabilitas transaksi lintas batas di Indonesia.</p><p data-block-id=\"afbb93b3-4f91-49c2-bd54-ea8a525148ee\">Saat pelanggan memilih Hana VA saat checkout, mereka akan menerima nomor virtual account yang unik. Mereka kemudian dapat menyelesaikan pembayaran melalui aplikasi mobile banking Hana Bank, platform internet banking, ATM, atau di lokasi cabang Hana Bank mana pun. Pembayaran akan dikonfirmasi secara otomatis setelah pelanggan mentransfer jumlah yang sesuai ke nomor virtual account yang diberikan.</p><hr class=\"hr-divider1\"><h2 data-block-id=\"6146dcc6-4245-4158-a034-de0971f8c50b\">Fitur</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"523\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:523px;width:523px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:235px;\"><col style=\"width:288px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\"><p data-block-id=\"db4dfef8-c563-4305-8c29-ef2b1aa63d40\"><strong>Kode channel</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"288\"><p data-block-id=\"396eeeac-4ec3-4dcb-9d87-03dfbc708fe4\"><code>HANA_VIRTUAL_ACCOUNT</code></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\"><p data-block-id=\"05742465-0957-4c43-b4a1-a714d1ec5bd9\"><strong>Mata uang</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"288\"><p data-block-id=\"089d5743-8152-4ba6-8397-606b6cec62d6\">IDR</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\"><p data-block-id=\"216547ce-9149-4c98-863b-af7a9b417559\"><strong>Jumlah minimum</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"288\"><p data-block-id=\"9f11a493-657e-4f53-8200-664b29cbb4d0\">1</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\"><p data-block-id=\"917595fc-cd1e-4638-a3ac-8c763018c400\"><strong>Jumlah maksimum</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"288\"><p data-block-id=\"050f0c67-b03f-4f17-88cb-fe412010855b\">50,000,000,000</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\"><p data-block-id=\"dd693bd7-6fa5-470c-a762-3bd25581ee55\"><strong>Alur persetujuan pengguna</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"288\"><p data-block-id=\"6c3485e2-8be5-421b-8f58-5cffed379b08\">PRESENT TO CUSTOMER</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\"><p data-block-id=\"00b142a2-96d8-469f-a603-d7f653f2f6a6\"><strong>Kode pembayaran yang dapat digunakan kembali</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"288\"><p data-block-id=\"4539fce0-abba-4afc-a78b-9edd62506ad7\">✅</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\"><p data-block-id=\"a15e3b11-bb7c-4496-bbdd-cbc61b5faf78\"><strong>Kode pembayaran custom</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"288\"><p data-block-id=\"fee79fe7-3031-47a6-a8a4-e343701d0de7\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\"><p data-block-id=\"d4fc461e-77d4-4e93-b6a4-95652e301b57\"><strong>Tampilkan nama merchant</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"288\"><p data-block-id=\"7ee79971-f5d3-47f9-b56c-c662acc7bb3d\">MERCHANT</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\"><p data-block-id=\"260ee695-3783-478d-b6ce-168812cf5235\"><strong>Tampilkan nama pengguna</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"288\"><p data-block-id=\"c089f673-06d7-409d-a611-15d4b735faad\">✅</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\"><p data-block-id=\"ebe59eaf-3581-4b5e-9133-086846171bc3\"><strong>Atur kedaluwarsa</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"288\"><p data-block-id=\"12be7429-c7c7-4479-b81b-04da759b7fef\">✅</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\"><p data-block-id=\"7750e331-7b15-4423-9ba5-f771994775fe\"><strong>Waktu settlement</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"288\"><p data-block-id=\"cfc1be6f-af22-48f6-bbf6-534529b76da5\">Instan</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\"><p data-block-id=\"6779fc15-6426-43e4-83b0-b2e6307dba73\"><strong>Refund</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"288\"><p data-block-id=\"d6dac5f5-cc08-448c-a14b-4b4811a5274f\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\"><p data-block-id=\"0baabc7e-a92b-49d0-af45-796c16289f04\"><strong>Refund sebagian</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"288\"><p data-block-id=\"3db5ce35-df38-47d0-8955-bd2e0dbfbc23\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\"><p data-block-id=\"166f9598-76a9-48a7-b24b-9c06b9f896ce\"><strong>Refund sebagian berulang</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"288\"><p data-block-id=\"e0def918-8005-4a4e-b489-d49d65943b1a\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\"><p data-block-id=\"256467fa-b7fd-45f2-b88e-195088282404\"><strong>Validitas refund</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"288\"><p data-block-id=\"36880c22-7833-45f4-b3b2-ca7bb0454f6c\">N/A</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\"><p data-block-id=\"5c93e485-a74d-4a50-8a1b-9bba2a9f420b\"><strong>Integrasi yang kompatibel</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"288\"><p data-block-id=\"a65b438c-71f6-40d0-a937-5a7d8672ccf9\">Payment API, Payment Links</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"2b081c08-ffd2-493a-b253-c4931f5f1c75\">Cara membayar</h2><div class=\"details-wrapper details-wrapper_rendered\" data-type=\"details-wrapper\"><details data-opened=\"true\" data-button-align=\"right\" data-details-border=\"withBorder\" data-expand-icon=\"arrow\" data-lock=\"false\"><summary><p data-block-id=\"2489516d-1747-4d6a-a095-881709940e75\">Mobile banking</p></summary><div><div><ol data-block-id=\"cf040642-e442-46df-8880-55c9973f092a\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"fb36bac3-d049-4a41-ad7a-be653a95c497\"><p data-block-id=\"249aec70-31be-4e17-bd42-b0e4cce850fe\">Login ke aplikasi mobile LINE Bank</p></li><li data-block-id=\"740e71e2-f26a-40ac-81c5-88f7004aaa98\"><p data-block-id=\"639db83f-d2e4-4a10-916a-4e5137350287\">Pilih <strong>Top Up &amp; Bill &gt; Hana Bank Virtual Account</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"dcaa91e9-2062-450a-ae89-5cd0673683b2\"><p data-block-id=\"8a63d3cf-3a42-4c35-ae63-c9aa25058b46\">Masukkan nomor virtual account (contoh: 9010001112341234234)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"31329550-e8fe-411c-a270-d0f3ab256bd5\"><p data-block-id=\"76f8875b-88d5-413e-8c19-68ee923fd2a2\">Konfirmasi detail pembayaran</p></li><li data-block-id=\"e8368295-a0d0-4dad-bce3-c15e08b07a22\"><p data-block-id=\"5b32b875-dd48-4c15-92af-ca1016b01b9f\">Masukkan PIN</p></li></ol></div></div></details><button class=\"details-arrow\" type=\"details\"></button></div><p data-block-id=\"f6d84e8d-d1d9-4945-9916-4b63220d8b3d\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Akun Virtual Hana (pilot)","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"Hana Virtual Account (นำร่อง)","Slug":"hana-virtual-accounts","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"763c044f-d0be-4374-947c-7810d1cac1e3\"><img data-block-id=\"5b01429e-04c3-451e-a648-ee12ad99d661\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(69).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" title=\"image(69).png\" width=\"277\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:277px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"186bc212-4f89-4c6d-9d91-b52c32678e13\">Hana Virtual Account เป็นวิธีการชำระเงินที่เชื่อถือได้จากหนึ่งในเครือข่ายธนาคารระหว่างประเทศของอินโดนีเซีย ให้บริการโดย Hana Bank Indonesia ซึ่งเป็นบริษัทในเครือของ Hana Financial Group จากเกาหลีใต้ ซึ่งเป็นที่รู้จักในด้านบริการธนาคารสำหรับองค์กรที่แข็งแกร่งและความสามารถในการทำธุรกรรมข้ามพรมแดนในอินโดนีเซีย</p><p data-block-id=\"afbb93b3-4f91-49c2-bd54-ea8a525148ee\">เมื่อลูกค้าเลือก Hana VA ระหว่างการชำระเงิน พวกเขาจะได้รับหมายเลขบัญชีเสมือนที่ไม่ซ้ำกัน จากนั้นพวกเขาสามารถชำระเงินให้เสร็จสมบูรณ์ผ่านแอปพลิเคชันธนาคารบนมือถือของ Hana Bank, แพลตฟอร์มอินเทอร์เน็ตแบงก์กิ้ง, ตู้ ATM หรือที่สาขาของ Hana Bank ทุกแห่ง การชำระเงินจะได้รับการยืนยันโดยอัตโนมัติเมื่อลูกค้าโอนเงินตามจำนวนที่แน่นอนไปยังหมายเลขบัญชีเสมือนที่ให้ไว้</p><hr class=\"hr-divider1\"><h2 data-block-id=\"6146dcc6-4245-4158-a034-de0971f8c50b\">คุณสมบัติ</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"523\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:523px;width:523px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:235px;\"><col style=\"width:288px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"235\"><p data-block-id=\"db4dfef8-c563-4305-8c29-ef2b1aa63d40\"><strong>รหัสช่องทาง</strong></p></t